from gerco schot subject ray tracing pictures for those who are interested in ray traced pictures, there is a nice example on alt binaries pictures misc. the file is called poolball.gif. it shows a
pooltable with... yes! ... poolballs!
resolution: 1024x768, colours: 256 (only).
the tga (24 bit) version is also available, but a bit big (2.4mb) to post.
the picture is created with pov-ray. enjoy! _gerco_
